{"tid":423040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警屯門工廈偷260罐奶粉被捕","createTime":"2017-10-03T14:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T15:47:26.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f29f60e6f40f592d2822d4f2f2aee6ed1baf09e7","tid":423040,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"停職警變奶粉大盜　屯門工廈偷260罐奶粉被捕<br />\n<br />\n撰文：\t黃煒堯 發佈日期：2017-10-03 22:30 最後更新日期：2017-10-03 22:30<br />\n一名停職警察化身奶粉大盜！警方今日 (3日)於荃灣區拘捕一名正停職的男警，涉嫌於上月18日於屯門一工業大廈內企圖盜竊120罐奶粉，總值約25,000元，以及於25日偷走140罐奶粉，總值29000元。據知，該名男警早前已因涉及其他案件被停職。<br />\n<br />\n商罪科欠債「翻閹」警長　涉收錢放生「風化案」疑人被捕<br />\n男警認警署內偷同袍金錢　稱患抑鬱藉偷竊取舒暢感　官押後判刑<br />\n休班警召妓「撻朵」食「霸王餐」　行為失當罪成　上訴駁回"},{"pid":"d59acaefaeacd685d60aedc616a69f6511b7e5c1","tid":423040,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e73420cd6bedf0e4956b98045282a5c26a3acf","tid":423040,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重視</span></span>"},{"pid":"517b4db98907dba934230bd6347ae06a8025a0e5","tid":423040,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全港最大犯罪集團"},{"pid":"d7097cb183c5039b1df997ec731ca121f37360a2","tid":423040,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4dfb6ad04382a897f2108b024a98e830cbbc8a","tid":423040,"uid":44243,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:18:28.000Z","msg":